===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|网|維|t1=net|t2=bird (tied with string)|ls=ic}} — net for catching birds. The original version is [[𦌴]].

===Etymology 1===
{{zh-forms|s=罗|alt=𦋝,𦌴}}

Perhaps related to {{cog|bo|དྲ||net}}, {{m|bo|རྒྱ||net; trap}}, {{cog|txg|𗙲||net}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}; {{zh-ref|Hill, 2014}}; {{zh-ref|Jacques, 2014}}). From this, {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*C-raj}} can be reconstructed.

